"Chemical weapons?  Check.  Biological outbreak?  Check.  Nuclear war?  "
"Check.  Sounds like the perfect job for you!"
msgstr "化學武器？檢查。生物爆發？檢查。核戰爭？檢查。聽起來這工作正適合你！"

